  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb0\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bc7 \u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb0, \u0b85\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0bc2\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The voice of the people should be listened to and not oppressed",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "Instead of isolating the protesters, the government should respect their legitimate demands and carry out negotiations with them. The National Peace Council of Sri Lanka has urged that the government should listen to the voice of the people and not target and oppress the main members of the protest movement.",
        "In the media statement released by the Peace Council on Friday, it is stated that;",
        "Sri Lanka witnessed a political upheaval rarely seen in the world. An unarmed people's movement led by the people, for the people, forced the resignation of a president, a prime minister and a cabinet.",
        "It was seen that this protest movement attracted the attention of the international community due to its size, effectiveness and peacefulness. The reason for the success of the protest movement was its spontaneous and peaceful nature.",
        "The protest movement that emerged from the genuine grievances and problems of the people turned into a massive mass movement. The previous government refused to accept responsibility for the dangerous situation and failed to take necessary steps to resolve the crisis. The violence that may have taken place was initiated by the government in the first place.",
        "The new government that has just taken office under the leadership of a new president consists mostly of members of the cabinet that resigned in May 2022. This has fueled the protestors' discontent and hatred.",
        "The National Peace Council urges the government to thoroughly investigate the causes of the economic decline and take action against those responsible. The many failures the country has had to face due to misrule and corruption have made people lose faith in the current parliament. Therefore, we request the government to call an election as soon as possible to elect a new parliament with a new people's mandate.",
        "Instead of dealing with the root causes of the protests, we are deeply concerned that the government is targeting key members of the protest movement on flimsy charges under the Emergency Act, which suspends existing laws and their protections.",
        "The government's position in the parliament appears to be strong, but its popular support is very weak, said Fitch Rating 2022 July 28, which evaluates the economic condition of the world's countries.",
        "So it is important that the government find ways to listen to their legitimate demands and engage with them in a meaningful way instead of isolating them."
      ],
